data.description: This home is stunning! Almost new, 2500+ sq ft, 3 BR, 2 1/2 BA 2-story home with a huge 2-floor loft. Open first-floor plan with 9 ft ceilings & 2-story foyer. The floor plan offers a 1-floor den with full-view French doors, formal dining room, well-appointed gourmet kitchen loaded with white shaker cabinets, all stainless appliances, center island & quartz tops, a breakfast dinette & a cozy family room with a gas log fireplace. The 2nd floor offers a convenient laundry room, and all 3 BRs including the grand primary suite that offers coffered ceilings, a walk-in closet, and full bath. Additional upgrades & extras include wainscoting, 2-panel white doors, concrete patio with firepit & so much more. Transferable Builder warranty. Attention Agents: See ATA remarks & offer instruction docs.
